P\left(X_n=0 \right)
 P\left(X_n=0 \right)= \sum\left[ {\frac12}^s {\frac12}^r {\frac12}^e {\frac12}^r : s+2r+e=n, e \ne 0 \text{ iff } r \ne 0 \right]. 
n \geq 1
\mathrm{Pr}[X_n=0]=0.5
\mathrm{Pr}[X_n=1]=0.5
n \geq 1
\mathrm{Pr}[X_n=0]=\begin{cases} 0.5 & \text{if } X_{n-1}=0 \\ 0.5 & \text{if } X_{n-1}=1 \end{cases}
\mathrm{Pr}[X_n=1]=\begin{cases} 0.5 & \text{if } X_{n-1}=0 \\ 0.5 & \text{if } X_{n-1}=1. \end{cases}
